'''Maurizio "Zanza" Zanfanti''' (20 October 1955 - 26 September 2018) was an Italian [[Playboy lifestyle|playboy]] who operated in [[Rimini]] and claimed to have slept with 6,000 women and to have done more for the [[Italian Riviera]] than "100 tourist agencies".<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/a-passionate-farewell-to-maurizio-zanfanti-the-last-latin-lover-06fglhtm3|title=A passionate farewell to Maurizio Zanfanti, the last Latin lover|first=Tom|last=Kington|date=28 September 2018|work=The Times}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/obituaries/2018/10/03/maurizio-zanza-zanfanti-legendary-playboy-rimini-obituary/|title=Maurizio ‘Zanza’ Zanfanti, legendary playboy from Rimini – obituary|date=3 October 2018|work=The Daily Telegraph}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.corriere.it/cronache/18_settembre_26/morto-zanza-re-playboy-rimini-stroncato-un-malore-mentre-era-una-23enne-2f90405e-c164-11e8-bcc0-6fbb0e9f9aa8.shtml|title=Morto «Zanza», re dei playboy di Rimini: colpito da malore|first=Claudio|last=Del Frate|work=Corriere della Sera|language=it}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ilfattoquotidiano.it/2018/09/26/rimini-e-morto-maurizio-zanfanti-detto-zanza-il-re-dei-vitelloni-romagnoli-aveva-sedotto-6mila-donne/4650801/|title=Maurizio Zanfanti, morto Zanza il re dei vitelloni romagnoli: era appartato con una 23enne|work=Il Fatto Quotidiano|date=26 September 2018|language=it}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.tpi.it/2018/09/28/maurizio-zanfanti-zanza/|title=Chi era Zanza, il "re dei vitelloni" delle notti brave in Riviera|date=28 September 2018|publisher=TPI|language=it}}</ref> He died from a [[Myocardial infarction]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://metro.co.uk/2018/09/28/romeo-of-rimini-playboy-maurizio-zanfanti-dies-while-having-sex-with-tourist-23-7986557/|title=Man who had sex with 6,000 women dies while having sex with tourist|date=28 September 2018|work=Metro}}</ref>
